HEADWORD: Matchlock
<hw>Match"lock`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An old form of
gunlock containing a match for firing the priming; hence, a musket fired
by means of a match.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

